---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Townfield Allotments and our community"
>
  <style>
    .about-section {
      background-color: var(--white);
    }

    .about-content {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .about-content p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .about-image {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), var(--primary));
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      padding: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--white);
      height: 350px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 5rem;
    }

    .community-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-light), var(--accent));
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .values-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .value-card {
      background-color: var(--white);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    }

    .value-card h3 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .value-card p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .timeline {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .timeline-year {
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    .timeline-content {
      background-color: var(--bg-light);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }

    .timeline-content h4 {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .timeline-content p {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .about-content,
      .community-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .about-image {
        height: 250px;
        font-size: 4rem;
      }

      .timeline-item {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .community-stats {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>About Townfield Allotments</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        A thriving community dedicated to growing food and building connections
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h3
        style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
      >
        Our Story
      </h3>
      <div class="about-content">
        <div>
          <p>
            Frodsham Townfield Allotments offer plots to rent for vegetable
            growing and keeping chickens – along the same lines as a traditional
            allotment. We believe growing your own food should be accessible to
            everyone, regardless of experience level or available time.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our plots are located in a beautiful field at the top of Langdale
            Way on the junction with Town-field Lane. Whether you're looking for
            a small space to experiment or a full plot to really develop your
            growing skills, we have something perfect for you.
          </p>
          <p>
            The allotments are let by Atlantic Hardware, the land owners, with
            the Association of Frodsham Townfield Allotments (AFTA) managing the
            lettings and site maintenance on their behalf.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="about-image">🌾</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Community Stats -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h3
        style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
      >
        By The Numbers
      </h3>
      <div class="community-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">~50</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Active Plotholders</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">All</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Ages Welcome</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">115</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Max Plot Size (m²)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">24/7</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Site Access</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h3
        style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
      >
        Our Values
      </h3>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>
            We're more than plotholders – we're friends and neighbors working
            together to create something special.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Accessibility</h3>
          <p>
            Everyone is welcome, from complete beginners to experienced
            gardeners, from young families to pensioners.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Sustainability</h3>
          <p>
            Growing your own food, reducing waste, and connecting with nature
            are at the heart of what we do.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Excellence</h3>
          <p>
            We maintain high standards for our site and support our plotholders
            in achieving their growing goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Flexibility</h3>
          <p>
            Whether you want a small half plot or a full plot, we adapt to your
            needs as your passion grows.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Support</h3>
          <p>
            New to allotments? Our experienced community is here to help you
            succeed from day one.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AFTA -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h3
        style="color: var(--primary); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
      >
        About AFTA
      </h3>
      <p
        style="color: var(--text-light); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;"
      >
        The Association of Frodsham Townfield Allotments (AFTA) is the
        organization that manages the day-to-day operations of our allotments on
        behalf of the land owner, Atlantic Hardware.
      </p>

      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Plot Management</h3>
          <p>
            AFTA handles all lettings and ensures fair access to plots for all
            members of the community.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Site Maintenance</h3>
          <p>
            We oversee paths, communal areas, and ensure the site remains safe
            and well-maintained.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <h3>Community Events</h3>
          <p>
            We organize gatherings and events to bring our plotholders together
            and share experiences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
